<h1 class="mainheader">MycoKeyCreator</h1>
<p>
    MycoKeyCreator is a free software package for the creation and maintenance of online fungi
    keys.
</p>
<p>
    A desktop application allows the user to create and edit the keys.
</p>


<ul class="nav nav-pills mb-3" id="myTab" role="tablist">
    <li class="nav-item">
        <a class="nav-link active" id="keys-tab" data-toggle="pill" href="#keys" role="tab" aria-controls="keys" aria-selected="true">Key List</a>
    </li>
    <li class="nav-item">
        <a class="nav-link" id="keyeditor-tab" data-toggle="pill" href="#keyeditor" role="tab" aria-controls="keyeditor" aria-selected="true">Key Editor</a>
    </li>
    <li class="nav-item">
        <a class="nav-link" id="keysummary-tab" data-toggle="pill" href="#keysummary" role="tab" aria-controls="keysummary" aria-selected="true">Summary Editor</a>
    </li>
    <li class="nav-item">
        <a class="nav-link" id="attributes-tab" data-toggle="pill" href="#attributes" role="tab" aria-controls="attributes" aria-selected="false">Attributes Editor</a>
    </li>
    <li class="nav-item">
        <a class="nav-link" id="speciesattributes-tab" data-toggle="pill" href="#speciesattributes" role="tab" aria-controls="speciesattributes" aria-selected="false">Species Attributes Editor</a>
    </li>
</ul>

<div class="tab-content" id="nav-tabContent">
    <div class="tab-pane fade show active" id="keys" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="keys-tab">
        <p>
            The user can add, edit and delete keys:
        </p>
        <p>
            @{
                <img src="/Images/Keys.png" style="margin-left:30px; margin-right:30px;" border="0">
            }
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="tab-pane fade" id="keyeditor" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="keyeditor-tab">
        <p>
            The user can open a key for editing:
        </p>
        <p>
            @{
                <img src="/Images/KeyEditor.png" style="margin-left:30px; margin-right:30px;" border="0">
            }
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="tab-pane fade" id="keysummary" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="keysummary-tab">
        <p>
            The user can edit the summary information:
        </p>
        <p>
            @{
                <img src="/Images/KeySummary.png" style="margin-left:30px; margin-right:30px;" border="0">
            }
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="tab-pane fade" id="attributes" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="attributes-tab">
        <p>
            The user can create attributes:
        </p>
        <p>
            @{
                <img src="/Images/AttributeEditor.png" style="margin-left:30px; margin-right:30px;" border="0">
            }
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="tab-pane fade" id="speciesattributes" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="speciesattributes-tab">
        <p>
            And then assign attributes to each species:
        </p>
        <p>
            @{
                <img src="/Images/SpeciesAttributesEditor.png" style="margin-left:30px; margin-right:30px;" border="0">
            }
        </p>
    </div>
</div>

<p>
    It is written in C# and .Net and runs on a Windows PC.
</p>
<p>
    A web application creates a web site - such as this one - with the online keys.
    It is written in Asp.Net Core.
</p>
<p>
    The keys are stored in a Microsoft SQLServer database.
</p>
<p>
    You are welcome to use the software to create your own web site. You will of course have to edit
    some pages to suit your needs. Alternatively you can create a database, and I will add it to
    this web site. There is currently no documentation available: I will create some as and when it is
    needed. The software is still in development.
</p>
